<h2>Step 4: Use HowTo Schema for Procedural Content</h2>
<p>HowTo schema marks up step-by-step instructions in a format AI systems can parse, reorder, and cite as numbered procedures. It is essential for guides, tutorials, recipes, and any content that teaches a process.</p>
<h3>HowTo Schema Structure</h3>
<pre><code class="language-json">&#123;
  &quot;@context&quot;: &quot;https://schema.org&quot;,
  &quot;@type&quot;: &quot;HowTo&quot;,
  &quot;name&quot;: &quot;How to Implement Schema Markup for AI Agents&quot;,
  &quot;description&quot;: &quot;A step-by-step guide to adding structured data that AI search engines can read and cite.&quot;,
